Le Comptoir – What it is
	•	Welcome & manage visitors at IT support counters
	•	Queue management: register, wait, be assigned to a coach
	•	Support handling: incidents, onboarding, information, hardware returns
	•	Integration with ServiceNow for ticket creation & follow-up
	•	Dashboards & KPIs in Power BI for activity monitoring

⸻

